attr.title: GUM GIRL Gameboy Edition
attr.desc: Use your bubble gum to create temporary platforms to solve puzzles and traverse through the cosmic Starbase. Defeat the treacherous drill in order to save your solar system.
attr.inst:
Download from CasePortman https://caseportman.itch.io/gumgirl
Locate data.win file and place into gamedata folder.
